item.description:
Join us for dinner at the Red Fez before we head to karaoke. This is a joint event with the Boston International Dining Out Meet Up group. Red Fez is known for its Middle Eastern and Mediterranean cuisine. The restaurant offers free parking for guests! Join us for a delicious dinner with fun and friendly people!
If you have trouble finding our group please call Catherine at 774 232 0000.
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Catherine (see photo) inside ent. If need to, please call 774 232 0000
item.name: Pre- Karaoke Dinner at Red Fez, Boston. Joint Event
